description: This file implements the creation function for a TLS CipherSwitch object in the context of a Transport Layer Security (TLS) implementation. It primarily contains a function that wraps the instantiation of the CipherSwitch object via TlsCsoCreate, along with license and module documentation.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE TlsCreateCipherSwitch(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new TLS CipherSwitch object, taking in container, owner, and reserved context handles.
